title: Windows 7 Theme - For Windows XP and Vista
description:
This Theme is free.

That means you don't have to pay and you don't break any laws :D

Don't worry, there isn't any password !



To install the Theme you need to:

Click on the file "Seven" or "Seven.msstyles" in "Windows 7" folder, 
and when the appearance window comes, select the theme and press OK.


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Ovoj program e besplaten t.s. FREE.

Toa znaci deka ne se placa i ne prekrsuvame nikakov zakon.

Pa luge navalete :D

Ova e vsusnost tema za Windows XP ili Vista, temata se vika Window 7 i e Extra !
